titles.title: To extend the existing temporary duty suspension on o-Cumyl-octylphenol.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

committee.name: House Committee on Ways and Means

bill.summary: 5/14/2003--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 2005, the existing temporary duty suspension on o-Cumyl-octylphenol.
